{
 "name": "RPlog_Introduction_to_Serenella",
 "title": "Introduction to Serenella",
 "summary": "In the meditation spire of the New Alderaan Jedi Temple, the pregnant performer Serenella Jordain agrees with Luke Skywalker that her Force-sensitive daughter Tara should be raised among the Jedi, even as she yearns to return to her singing and acting career. Luke privately struggles with concern for the child, whose father is the fallen Dareus, now Malign's apprentice. Sabrina Rheatis arrives and is introduced to Serenella, learning that the temple may soon shelter two Sith offspring. After Serenella waddles off to rest, Luke and Sabrina speak frankly about the gathering danger and their shared resolve, reaffirming their bond and Sabrina's wish to resume her studies under Luke as the conflict ahead looms.",
